hackathon-description-text: The closing pitches will be open to everyone and we strongly encourage everyone to come cheer on their favorite Blue Devils as they showcase their final apps!
hackathon-requirements:
If you made a native Objective-C app, include an archive of your Xcode project.
If you did website, include the URL to where it is hosted or the front-end HTML files.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: 13" MacBook Air (128 GB) for each member of the team (up to 3 members) that has the best use of the iTunes Store Catalog.
hackathon-prizes.prize-title: Best use of the iTunes Store Catalog

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: 64 GB iPad Mini (Wi-Fi) for the team that creates the best native iOS (Objective-C) app
13" MacBook Air (128 GB) for each member of the team (up to 3 members) that has the best use of AT&T-provided APIs
64 GB iPad Mini (Wi-Fi) and $500 in Visa Gift Cards for each member of the team (up to 3 members) as voted on by the audience at the final presentations
